name: WestJet Unveils NEW 'Elevation Lounge' at Calgary Airport
description:
After two years in the making, WestJet finally revealed brand new Elevation Lounge, at their home base of Calgary International Airport! This is a pretty big step for them and it was quite the project, but it looks fantastic!

Big thank you to WestJet for inviting me to come check it out!
